<div class="w-990">
<div class="polysemy"><p class="f14" id="unifypromptone">
				   “<a href="/wiki/%E3%80%8A%E9%BC%B9%E9%BC%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%8B">《鼹鼠的故事》</a>”是“<a href="/wiki/%E9%BC%B9%E9%BC%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B">鼹鼠的故事</a>”的同义词。</p></div>
